My therapist said this to me “just know that everything you normally struggle with is going to be on steroids because of this shit”.  Ok he didn’t say “this shit” but I put that in there for you :).  It did help me to know that yes, this is harder than normal.  The feelings of the increased difficulty are real and fact based.  And.  I’m hoping all the best for you my friend.  We got this.
I’m sorry friend.  I would wear the glitter top hat for you.
